title: Spliced Business Formations within 8 Quarters for Tennessee (DISCONTINUED)
notes:
The Business Formation Statistics are now released on a monthly basis, and the quarterly series will no longer be updated. See BFSBF8QTOTALSATN (https://fred.stlouisfed.org/series/BFSBF8QTOTALSATN) for an alternative.

This series combines (splices) https://fred.stlouisfed.org/series/BF8QSATN and https://fred.stlouisfed.org/series/PBF8QSATN to provide the entire time series for the actual and projected business formations within 8 quarters.
